title: Make Like a Kid Again
description:
When’s the last time you DIYed, baked or planted? For most of us, the answer is more than a while ago, but that wasn’t always the case. When we were little, we made things all the time and were proud of what we made.

But then something changed.

See what can happen when folks leave their excuses behind and start making again. Then, give it a try yourself on December 17th for Make Something Day.
